《1080°》普遍获得评论称赞，在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]和[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]上的汇总得分为88/100和90%<ref name="GameRankings">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamerankings.com/n64/196500-1080-teneighty-snowboarding/index.html |title=1080 Snowboarding |publisher=[[Game_Rankings|Game Rankings]] |accessdate=2007-04-17 |archive-date=2009-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090317055939/http://www.gamerankings.com/n64/196500-1080-teneighty-snowboarding/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="MetaCritic">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/n64/1080snowboarding |title=1080° Snowboarding |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080624073046/http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/n64/1080snowboarding |archivedate=2008-06-24 |accessdate=2010-08-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。游戏赢得[[互动艺术与科学学会|互动艺术与科学学会]]的1999年年度游戏机体育类游戏奖<ref name="Award">{{cite web |url=http://www.interactive.org/awards/award_category_details.asp?idAward=1999&idGameAwardType=57 |title=Console Sports Game of the Year |publisher=Academy of Interactive Arts & Sciences |accessdate=2011-06-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080307095258/http://www.interactive.org/awards.php?winners&year=1999&cat=199925 |archivedate=2008-03-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，GameSpot称其为“在体育类和竞速类中都是最有价值的游戏之一”<ref name="GameSpot review" />。《1080°》被视为当时滑雪作品中的先导者，其“太棒了”，“让发行巨头[[艺电|艺电]]耗费数年并使用远为强劲的平台”，用[[SSX系列|SSX系列]]“作为强大竞争者”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://cube.ign.com/articles/442/442561p1.html |title=1080: Avalanche |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2007-05-16 |last=Casamassina |first=Matt |date=2003-12-01 |archive-date=2007-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070706140058/http://cube.ign.com/articles/442/442561p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]]》称赞其为“迄今最使人信服的电子游戏模拟滑雪体验”，和当时任天堂其他游戏“严肃的气氛”不同<ref name="Edge Review" />。

游戏图形为[[任天堂64|任天堂64]]当时的最高质量<ref name="Edge Review">{{Cite news |title =1080° Snowboarding |periodical=[[Edge_(magazine)|Edge]] |publisher = [[Future_Publishing|Future Publishing]] |pages = 86–88 |date = April 1998 | issue=57}}</ref><ref name="CVG" />。评论称赞游戏图形的一般性质，如清晰、细致、流畅、无多边形丢失<ref name="GameSpot review">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/n64/sports/1080snowboarding/review.html |title=1080:TenEighty Snowboarding |accessdate=2007-04-17 |last=Smith |first=Josh |date=1998-05-25 |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070517051036/http://www.gamespot.com/n64/sports/1080snowboarding/review.html |archivedate=2007-05-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="Gamebits" />。评论还特别称赞游戏的镜头应用，提到了游戏“非常坚实”物理模型<ref name="GameSpot review" />、赛手速度效果，以及游戏中雪的效果（雪对日光的反射适当，松软的雪和踩过的雪表现不同）<ref name="IGN rev" /><ref name="Gamebits">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamebits.net/n64/teneight/ |title=1080 SNOWBOARDING |accessdate=2007-04-17 |last=Gagne |first=Ken |date=1998-05-11 |publisher=Gamebits |archive-date=2007-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071225182432/http://www.gamebits.net/n64/teneight/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。评论指出的图形问题有，偶尔的弹出、错位的影子，以及竞速者通过赛道树时的延迟<ref name="IGN rev" />；这些一般被视为小问题<ref name="GameSpot review" />。

虽然《Edge》的评论积极，但认为游戏[[人工智能|人工智能]]（AI）存在问题；他们称《1080°》使用“作弊的”CPU对手<ref name="Edge Review" />。评论称AI单一且会在临近赛道终点时迅速追上玩家；他们还指出AI的“有限的一系列预定路线”，玩家可能知道AI会何时何地摔倒，“虽能带来超越电脑的机会，但难以从中获得满足”<ref name="Edge Review" />。《Edge》还称PAL版延迟“实在可笑”<ref name="PAL Edge Review">{{Cite news |title =1080° Snowboarding |periodical=[[Edge_(magazine)|Edge]] |publisher = [[Future_Publishing|Future Publishing]] |page = 96 |date = September 1998 | issue=62}}</ref>。他们确信，因为任天堂值得关注发行的衰落，“任何质量的作品都很可能轻易登顶榜单”<ref name="PAL Edge Review" />。

[[Allgame|Allgame]]认为《1080°》“高技术”的操作方式是游戏一大优势，虽然它开始很难<ref name="All Game Rev">{{cite web |url=http://www.allgame.com/game.php?id=7501 |title=1080° Snowboarding |accessdate=2007-04-17 |last=Sackenheim |first=Shawn |publisher=[[Allgame|Allgame]] |archive-date=2014-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141114211253/http://www.allgame.com/game.php?id=7501&tab=review |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[电脑与电子游戏|电脑与电子游戏]]》也称赞了操作方式，但不认同其难度，称“操作提供的如此出色，你单手在摇杆和Z键上就可能玩得非常好”<ref name="CVG">{{cite web|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/8317/reviews/1080-snowboarding-review/ |title=1080 Snowboarding |date=2001-08-15 |first=Alex |last=Constantides |accessdate=2007-12-26 |publisher=Computer and Video Games |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120225201756/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/8317/reviews/1080-snowboarding-review/ |archivedate=2012-02-25 }}</ref>。<!-- GameSpot called the game's control "thoroughly involving" and said that "the crouch move alone – which makes for supertight turns – makes this fun to play"<ref name="GameSpot review" />。 -->音乐通常获得称赞，IGN称其为“可以在此格式的所达杰出例子”<ref name="IGN rev" />，Allgame亦称其为“迄今最佳的N64原声”<ref name="All Game Rev" />。然而《Gamebits》认为原声简单而不足<ref name="Gamebits" />。《1080°》获得评论“相当完美音效”的称赞<ref name="All Game Rev" /><ref name="Gamebits" />。

在《[[官方任天堂杂志|官方任天堂杂志]]》2006年的怀旧评论中，史蒂夫·加勒特称《1080°》应“以电子游戏中对雪的最佳呈现而自豪”，同时还衬以“嗖嗖”的音效。他同时还称赞了多人模式的处理手法和质量。在总结中加勒特称，他确信“这好似真正的滑雪，特技表演自由、快速而且有趣”<ref name="retrospective">{{cite news |last=Jarratt |first=Steve |date=May 2006|work=Official Nintendo Magazine |title=What do you mean, you've never played 1080° Snowboarding |page=19 }}</ref>。杂志还将游戏列为第87大任天堂平台游戏。职员称其为最真实的滑雪游戏<ref>{{cite web |title=Nintendo Feature: 100 Best Nintendo Games: Part One |url=http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/7188/features/100-best-nintendo-games-part-one/ |work=[[Official_Nintendo_Magazine|Official Nintendo Magazine]] |last=East |first=Tom |date=2009-02-17 |accessdate=2013-12-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102063247/http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/7188/features/100-best-nintendo-games-part-one/ |archivedate=2013-11-02 }}</ref>。

《1080°》在日本售出2.3万<ref name="japansales">{{cite web |url=http://www.japan-gamecharts.com/n64.php |title=Nintendo 64 Japanese Ranking |publisher=Japan Game Charts |accessdate=2011-07-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090503110049/http://www.japan-gamecharts.com/n64.php |archivedate=2009-05-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，在美国售出123万<ref name="magicbox">{{cite web |url=http://www.the-magicbox.com/Chart-USPlatinum.shtml |title=US Platinum Videogame Chart |accessdate=2007-04-17 |publisher=The Magic Box |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070106203333/http://www.the-magicbox.com/Chart-USPlatinum.shtml |archivedate=2007-01-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。然而和开发团队第一款游戏《[[水上摩托64|水上摩托64]]》——日本销量15.4万，美国销量195万——相比<ref name="japansales" /><ref name="magicbox" />，游戏没有如此成功。2001年，《1080°》中滑雪者之一木町剑介，作为出来乱一下人物在《[[任天堂明星大乱斗DX|任天堂明星大乱斗DX]]》中登场<ref>{{cite web |url=http://cube.gamespy.com/gamecube/super-smash-bros-melee/guide/page_54.html |title=Text List |work=Super Smash Bros Arena |publisher=Gamespy |accessdate=2011-06-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080704141857/http://cube.gamespy.com/gamecube/super-smash-bros-melee/guide/page_54.html |archivedate=2008-07-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。游戏续作《[[1080°雪崩|1080°雪崩]]》于2003年在[[任天堂GameCube|任天堂GameCube]]上发行。《雪崩》受到相对的批评，在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的得分为73/100<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/gamecube/1080avalanche/ |title=1080° Avalanche |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080516145503/http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/gamecube/1080avalanche/ |archivedate=2008-05-16 |accessdate=2010-08-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，GameSpot称其“帧率有问题且游戏形态有限”<ref name="Gamespot Ava">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/1080-avalanche-review/1900-6085005 |title=1080 Avalanche |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |first=Greg |last=Kasavin |authorlink=Greg Kasavin |date=2003-12-03 |accessdate=2007-04-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160109125332/http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/1080-avalanche-review/1900-6085005/ |archivedate=2016-01-09 }}</ref>。《1080°》于任天堂[[Wii|Wii]] [[Virtual_Console|Virtual Console]]服务上再版，日版2008年1月15日发行，欧洲版2008年1月18日发行，北美版2008年1月28日发行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nintendo.co.jp/wii/vc/lineup.html |title=Virtual Console |publisher=Nintendo |accessdate=2008-01-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120809062156/http://www.nintendo.co.jp/wii/vc/lineup.html |archivedate=2012-08-09 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

